title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-5.6 - Project Classification
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 646-5.6 - Project Classification

State Regulations

Minor and Major project classifications established in 6
NYCRR
646-4.7
shall apply to any project that requires a permit pursuant to
this Article. Notes

§§
646-5.6

Adopted

New

York State Register March 17, 2021/Volume XLIII, Issue 11, eff. 3/17/2021

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
